connect to database : 

    sudo docker exec -it nimbuslance_db psql -U postgres -d nimbuslance

check table on database :

    \dt

migrate database :

    npx prisma migrate dev --name <name>
    npx prisma generate

    if any issues (onyl Dev) : 
        npx prisma migrate reset

exec cmd on container : 

    sudo docker exec -it docker-backend-1 <cmd>

check route mapping : 

  sudo docker logs docker-backend-1 | grep "Mapped"

check backend logs : 

    sudo docker logs docker-backend-1 --tail 50